'''Takoradi Technical Institute''' is a mixed school found in [[Takoradi]].The school was established in 1982 with the collaboration of the Ghanaian Government and German Government Support for Technical Cooperation.<ref>{{cite web|title=Takoradi Technical Institute|url=http://www.takoraditech.org/|website=Takoradi Technical Institute|accessdate=5 September 2015}}</ref> The school is popular for its facilities which is used to train the student and enhance the technical skills of the students,this training makes the student the best in terms of practical among all school in Takoradi.
